title: 1 - Dan Soder
itunes:title: 1 - Dan Soder
description: From Sirius XM's "The Bonfire," Showtime's "Billions," Comedy's "Stand-up," and Colorado's "Denver" comes Dan Soder. We talk about everything from legally smoking weed to illegally consuming Rolling Rock and Wild Turkey. It's a hell of a wild (turkey) ride. Here's five words to describe this episode: you are gonna love it.
